製造一個至[[數學評論]]的連結，僅需要一個參數 id。

語法：

 <nowiki>{{MathSciNet | id = 96d:11071}}</nowiki>

或可簡寫為

 <nowiki>{{MR|96d:11071}}</nowiki>


例子（引用期刊）：
 <nowiki>{{cite journal
  | author = Wiles, Andrew
  | title = Modular elliptic curves and Fermat's last theorem
  | journal = Annals of Mathematics
  | volume = 141
  | year = 1995
  | issue = 3
  | pages = 443–551
  | id = {{MathSciNet | id = 96d:11071}}}}</nowiki>

結果將是：
 {{cite journal
  | author = Wiles, Andrew
  | title = Modular elliptic curves and Fermat's last theorem
  | journal = Annals of Mathematics
  | volume = 141
  | year = 1995
  | issue = 3
  | pages = 443–551
  | id = [[數學評論|MR]][http://www.ams.org/mathscinet-getitem?mr=96d:11071 96d:11071]}}

